[00:32:18.000 --> 00:32:20.000]  明句
[00:32:20.000 --> 00:32:22.000]  是這樣說的
[00:32:22.000 --> 00:32:24.000]  Madness of all
[00:32:24.000 --> 00:32:26.000]  is to see the world
